	<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #ffffff;">The "</span><strong style="color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; text-align: left; background-color: #ffffff;">tray"</strong><span style="color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; text-align: left; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp;that appears at the bottom of the website when you are logged in, contains a marvellous developer utility called the "Webskin Tracer". You can activate it for any page by simply selecting the webskin tracer option.</span><span style="text-align: left; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; background-color: #ffffff;">The entire page's composite of views is laid bare; highlighting each webskin executed for the page. Select a specific view and the HTML fragment is highlighted, with a tooltip detailing exactly where the webskin template can be found.</span></p>
<p><div class='p_embed p_image_embed'>
<a href="http://getfile5.posterous.com/getfile/files.posterous.com/farcry/J3zi3kj5QyJX50N41UP3bz4QvoHmBzZG26bnayQWokFUTZq0YR9TZzJIAFSC/tracer01.png"><img alt="Tracer01" height="437" src="http://getfile6.posterous.com/getfile/files.posterous.com/farcry/scH4T2IOZb7rTq8rOhbquTrU2zAHcck55QqqmY3heklFXTUNdMqo7K961Rcf/tracer01.png.scaled.500.jpg" width="500" /></a>
</div>
<div class='p_embed p_image_embed'>
<a href="http://getfile1.posterous.com/getfile/files.posterous.com/farcry/DZpYHuMUFhNShxEivmsRztA9f5nE9NdLa8u9hyhLZBHzGV3DPXvfgN5wDAqf/tracer02.png.scaled.1000.jpg"><img alt="Tracer02" height="373" src="http://getfile9.posterous.com/getfile/files.posterous.com/farcry/KL44miGSxUirohfBT8qN329LTFlDuokLSu6jMXBPRpVmhDkNHbV7chSMcNyr/tracer02.png.scaled.500.jpg" width="500" /></a>
</div>
</p>
<p><span style="color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px;">You can turn on the webskin tracer without being logged in by using your project's "secret key" on the URL:&nbsp;<br /></span><a href="http://localhost:8888/index.cfm?objectid=E689D721-B6C9-605B-DE1D813E4CDA3339&amp;tracewebskins=secretkey" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px;">http://localhost:8888/index.cfm?objectid=E689D721-B6C9-605B-DE1D813E4CDA3339&amp;tracewebskins=secretkey</a></p>]]></content:encoded>
